Instructions for use:


Unzip the file project
Navigate to the project directory 
Run python3 A1_main.py 
Select Start Game
(Enemies are purple, Potions are red)

Movement
Press q button for automatic mode, including automatic movement
If q is not pressed, use the directional buttons to move the player
Press q again to halt the automatic mode, this will happen once the current action is completed
	Battle
Press a to attack 

Hover the mouse over an enemy or potion to show the value grid. 
Press the escape key to exit the game 
If you have died select restart to immediately play again, main menu to return to the start screen again and quit to exit the program 


Run A1_test.py to get test results 

